# KEEP THESE (Explicitly don't ignore)
# ============================================================================
!.gitkeep
!data/emission_factors/defra_2024.json  # Free, public data
!data/emission_factors/epa_2024.json  # Free, public data
!data/examples/  # Example data files are OK
!schemas/  # JSON schemas should be committed
!rules/  # Validation rules should be committed
!templates/  # Email templates should be committed
